{
  "__comment": "Dashboard de observabilidade do sistema distribuído de venda de ingressos. Gerado para ser provisionado automaticamente via infra/grafana/provisioning/dashboards/dashboard.yml. Métricas originadas do middleware prom-client em cada microsserviço.",

  "annotations": {
    "list": [
      {
        "builtIn": 1,
        "datasource": { "type": "grafana", "uid": "-- Grafana --" },
        "enable": true,
        "hide": true,
        "iconColor": "rgba(0, 211, 255, 1)",
        "name": "Annotations & Alerts",
        "type": "dashboard"
      }
    ]
  },

  "description": "Visão geral do sistema de venda de ingressos — taxa de requisições, erros, latência P95 e status dos serviços",
  "editable": true,
  "graphTooltip": 1,
  "id": null,
  "links": [],

  "panels": [

    {
      "__comment": "Painel 1 — Taxa de requisições por serviço. Query: rate() da métrica http_requests_total (Counter) agrupado pelo label 'job' (nome do serviço definido no prometheus.yml). Unidade reqps = requisições por segundo.",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "pointSize": 5,
            "showPoints": "never",
            "spanNulls": false,
            "axisBorderShow": false,
            "axisPlacement": "auto",
            "barAlignment": 0,
            "gradientMode": "none",
            "insertNulls": false,
            "lineInterpolation": "linear",
            "scaleDistribution": { "type": "linear" },
            "stacking": { "group": "A", "mode": "none" },
            "thresholdsStyle": { "mode": "off" }
          },
          "unit": "reqps",
          "mappings": [],
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "calcs": ["mean", "max"],
          "displayMode": "table",
          "placement": "bottom",
          "showLegend": true
        },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "desc" }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
          "expr": "sum(rate(http_requests_total[5m])) by (job)",
          "legendFormat": "{{job}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Taxa de Requisições por Serviço (req/s)",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },

    {
      "__comment": "Painel 2 — Taxa de erros HTTP 4xx e 5xx por serviço. Duas queries separadas permitem distinguir erros de cliente (4xx) de erros de servidor (5xx). O label status_code é preenchido com res.statusCode no middleware do prom-client.",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "pointSize": 5,
            "showPoints": "never",
            "spanNulls": false,
            "axisBorderShow": false,
            "axisPlacement": "auto",
            "barAlignment": 0,
            "gradientMode": "none",
            "insertNulls": false,
            "lineInterpolation": "linear",
            "scaleDistribution": { "type": "linear" },
            "stacking": { "group": "A", "mode": "none" },
            "thresholdsStyle": { "mode": "off" }
          },
          "unit": "reqps",
          "mappings": [],
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null },
              { "color": "red", "value": 0.01 }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 0 },
      "id": 2,
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "calcs": ["mean", "max"],
          "displayMode": "table",
          "placement": "bottom",
          "showLegend": true
        },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "desc" }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
          "expr": "sum(rate(http_requests_total{status_code=~\"4..\"}[5m])) by (job)",
          "legendFormat": "{{job}} — 4xx",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
          "expr": "sum(rate(http_requests_total{status_code=~\"5..\"}[5m])) by (job)",
          "legendFormat": "{{job}} — 5xx",
          "refId": "B"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Taxa de Erros por Serviço (4xx e 5xx)",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },

    {
      "__comment": "Painel 3 — Latência P95 por serviço. histogram_quantile(0.95, ...) calcula o percentil 95 a partir dos buckets do Histogram http_request_duration_seconds. Agrupa por (le, job): 'le' é o label de bucket obrigatório para histogram_quantile, 'job' identifica o serviço. Limiares: amarelo > 500ms, vermelho > 1s.",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "pointSize": 5,
            "showPoints": "never",
            "spanNulls": false,
            "axisBorderShow": false,
            "axisPlacement": "auto",
            "barAlignment": 0,
            "gradientMode": "none",
            "insertNulls": false,
            "lineInterpolation": "linear",
            "scaleDistribution": { "type": "linear" },
            "stacking": { "group": "A", "mode": "none" },
            "thresholdsStyle": { "mode": "line+area" }
          },
          "unit": "s",
          "mappings": [],
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null },
              { "color": "yellow", "value": 0.5 },
              { "color": "red", "value": 1 }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 8 },
      "id": 3,
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "calcs": ["mean", "max"],
          "displayMode": "table",
          "placement": "bottom",
          "showLegend": true
        },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "desc" }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum(rate(http_request_duration_seconds_bucket[5m])) by (le, job))",
          "legendFormat": "{{job}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Latência P95 por Serviço (segundos)",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },

    {
      "__comment": "Painel 4 — Status dos serviços (up/down). A métrica 'up' é gerada automaticamente pelo Prometheus para cada target configurado no prometheus.yml: valor 1 quando o scrape foi bem-sucedido, 0 quando falhou. O filtro por job exclui targets de infraestrutura (prometheus, grafana). Tipo 'stat' exibe um card por série com cor de fundo.",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "thresholds" },
          "mappings": [
            {
              "options": {
                "0": { "color": "red",   "index": 0, "text": "DOWN" },
                "1": { "color": "green", "index": 1, "text": "UP"   }
              },
              "type": "value"
            }
          ],
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "red",   "value": null },
              { "color": "green", "value": 1    }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 8 },
      "id": 4,
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "none",
        "justifyMode": "center",
        "orientation": "horizontal",
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": ["lastNotNull"],
          "fields": "",
          "values": false
        },
        "textMode": "auto"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
          "expr": "up{job=~\"auth-service|event-service|order-service|payment-service|notification-service\"}",
          "legendFormat": "{{job}}",
          "refId": "A",
          "instant": true
        }
      ],
      "title": "Status dos Serviços",
      "type": "stat"
    }

  ],

  "refresh": "30s",
  "schemaVersion": 38,
  "tags": ["ticket-system", "observabilidade"],
  "templating": { "list": [] },
  "time": { "from": "now-1h", "to": "now" },
  "timepicker": {},
  "timezone": "browser",
  "title": "Ticket System — Visão Geral",
  "uid": "ticket-system-overview",
  "version": 1
}
